wingpanel-indicator-weather (0.4.0) bionic; urgency=medium

  * UI minor updates
  * Added last weather data refresh information to the popover widget
  * Renamed ON/OFF setting to 'Show indicator'
  * Added a manual weather information refresh button to the popover widget
  * Fixed weather data auto refresh and on indicator load since it was not working
  * Moved the weather information management logic to a separate class

